AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001006> "Project Collaboration is a collaboration process in which multiple entities contribute expertise, resources, and labor toward the successful completion of a specific project.")
SubClassOf(<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001006> <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001003>)

