AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001007> "Joint Efforting is a collaboration process in which multiple entities combine efforts, knowledge, or labor toward a common goal, often in research, policy-making, or community initiatives.")
SubClassOf(<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001007> <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001003>)

# Class: <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001008> (joint servicing)

