AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001008> "Joint Servicing is a collaboration process in which two or more entities jointly provide or maintain a service, ensuring operational efficiency and shared responsibility.")
SubClassOf(<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001008> <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001003>)

