AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001009> "Alliancing is a collaboration process in which two or more entities form a long-term cooperative relationship based on shared objectives, often in research, industry, or government sectors.")
SubClassOf(<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001009> <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001003>)

