AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001010> "parenting"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001010> "Partnering is a collaboration process in which two or more entities form a structured partnership to achieve specific research, business, or development goals.")
SubClassOf(<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001010> <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001003>)

# Class: <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001012> (date process ended)

