EquivalentClasses(<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001015> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0020000> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000219> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000030>)))
SubClassOf(<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001015> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0020000>)

