AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001031> "A place that provides a controlled environment equipped with specialized instruments and facilities for conducting scientific research, experiments, measurements, and testing across various disciplines.")
